# INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS

Install dependencies:
sudo apt-get -y install build-essential cmake pkg-config libgsl-dev libblas3gf libblas-dev liblapack3gf liblapack-dev graphviz openscenegraph libopenscenegraph-dev gnuplot libgts-bin libcln6 libcln-dev ginac-tools libginac-dev



Compile library:

mkdir -p build && cd build
cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=.. ..
make
make install


